Here, the related files are mainly related to the air-sea flux calculation. In my PhD program, I have been working on this topic for a long time. 

Motion-Pack:
It includes how to remove the influences of platform. It will also introduce my experience and my trouble when I was doing this work.

Drag-Coefficient: 
It mainly refers to a modified equation which can be used to calculate Cd. COARE algorithm package is also included here for possible comparison. 

Gustiness: How I Analyze the Gustiness.

Updates will be followed.
